name: GazeboRoomRecipes
0:
”Alexa, open Gazebo Room Recipes.”
”Alexa, ask Gazebo Room Recipes for the latest recipes.”
”Alexa, ask Gazebo Room Recipes for Greek pasta salad recipes.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gazebo room recipes
des: With over 75 recipes on our website, we wanted to offer our customers an even easier way to find the very latest Gazebo Room Recipes. Now you can ask Alexa for the very latest recipes, submitted to us by our bloggers, social media followers, and even customers like you! Just say "Alexa, ask Gazebo Room Recipes for the latest recipes.", for a list of our most recent recipes, then say "Read me the first (second, third etc...) recipe." to have her read the entire recipe out loud to you.
